o-------------------o
| Installation help |
o-------------------o
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------o
|Browse to your steam folder                                                              |
|-> steamapps                                                                             |
|   ->"Your username"                                                                     |
|     -> Counter-Strike: Source                                                           |
|        -> cstrike                                                                       |
|           -> Maps                                                                       |
|              -> Copy dm_nova_final.bsp    AND    dm_nova_final.nav to your "maps" folder|
|                                                                                         |
o-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------o

About the map
o-------------o
> Supports 12 v 12 matches = 24 player maximum
> 2 main bases ( spawns )
> breakable windows
> openable metal doors in both bases
> team based colors
> poisoned pits ( 10 hp per tick )
> Roofs are accesible
> bridge between two bases ( from roof to roof )
> Find the rest by yourself...   :p
o-------------------------------------o

Thanks to

o-------------------------------------------------------------o

I hope you like this map and have fun!

-Biux aka. Biuxify
